Package ikor.collection Description

Main features:

  • Complete class hierarchy (vs. standard JCF): Collection < ( List, Dictionary, Relation ).
  • Separation of mutable and immutable collections, as in COCOA: X & MutableX.
  • Reference implementations based on JCF: StaticList (arrays), DynamicList (ArrayList) & DynamicDictionary (HashMap).
